OL,3,C'No quick fix,' to Lough Neagh crisis
OL,5,FIt resulted in bathing bans in some
OL,6,Fareas.
OL,8,FThe lough supplies 40% of Northern
OL,9,FIreland's drinking water and sustains
OL,10,Fa major eel-fishing industry.
OL,12,FMr Muir told MLAs on Tuesday that
OL,13,F"issues and challenges at Lough Neagh
OL,14,Fwill not be resolved overnight, nor
OL,15,Fwill they be resolved by my department
OL,16,Falone".
OL,18,F"They need a strategic, evidence based
OL,19,Fand across-government approach," he
OL,20,Fadded.
