OL,3,C'No quick fix,' to Lough Neagh crisis
OL,5,FThe ownership has been in the Earl of
OL,6,FShaftesbury's estate since the 1800s.
OL,7,FThe Earl recently said he "would like"
OL,8,Fto transfer it to a charity or
OL,9,Fcommunity trust model.
OL,11,FMr Muir said his personal preference
OL,12,F"is for community ownership".
